2025-03-02T10:11:14.839166Z  INFO docgen:   Line 8: **1. Introduction**
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839177Z  INFO docgen:   Line 9: 
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839187Z  INFO docgen:   Line 10: *   **1.1 Purpose:** This document outlines the requirements for the first version of Recipe Radar, a web application designed to help users discover recipes based on their available ingredients, dietary restrictions, and culinary preferences.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839199Z  INFO docgen:   Line 11: *   **1.2 Goals:**
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839209Z  INFO docgen:   Line 12:     *   Provide users with a seamless and intuitive recipe discovery experience.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839219Z  INFO docgen:   Line 13:     *   Reduce food waste by suggesting recipes based on ingredients users already have.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839229Z  INFO docgen:   Line 14:     *   Offer personalized recipe recommendations tailored to individual dietary needs and preferences.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839239Z  INFO docgen:   Line 15: 
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839249Z  INFO docgen:   Line 16: **2. User Personas (Example - To be expanded upon later)**
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839260Z  INFO docgen:   Line 17: 
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839270Z  INFO docgen:   Line 18: *   **The Busy Professional (Sarah):**  Limited time for cooking, wants quick and easy recipes using ingredients on hand.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839281Z  INFO docgen:   Line 19: *   **The Health-Conscious Cook (David):**  Specific dietary restrictions (e.g., gluten-free, vegan), interested in healthy and nutritious recipes.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839291Z  INFO docgen:   Line 20: 
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839302Z  INFO docgen:   Line 21: **3. User Stories and Features**
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839312Z  INFO docgen:   Line 22: 
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839324Z  INFO docgen:   Line 23: This section outlines the core user stories and features that address them. User stories are formatted as: "As a [user type], I want [goal] so that [benefit]."
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839335Z  INFO docgen:   Line 24: 
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839345Z  INFO docgen:   Line 25: *   **3.1 Ingredient-Based Recipe Search**
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839355Z  INFO docgen:   Line 26:     *   **User Story:** As a user, I want to input a list of ingredients I have available so that I can find recipes that use those ingredients.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839366Z  INFO docgen:   Line 27:     *   **Features:**
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839375Z  INFO docgen:   Line 28:         *   Ingredient input field (text-based with autocomplete suggestions based on a pre-defined ingredient database).
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839386Z  INFO docgen:   Line 29:         *   Ability to add multiple ingredients.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839397Z  INFO docgen:   Line 30:         *   "Find Recipes" button to initiate the search.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839407Z  INFO docgen:   Line 31:         *   Display of recipes that match the entered ingredients, ranked by relevance (number of matching ingredients, user ratings, etc.).
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839418Z  INFO docgen:   Line 32: *   **3.2 Dietary Restriction Filtering**
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839428Z  INFO docgen:   Line 33:     *   **User Story:** As a user with dietary restrictions, I want to filter recipes based on my restrictions (e.g., vegetarian, vegan, gluten-free) so that I only see recipes that are suitable for me.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839459Z  INFO docgen:   Line 34:     *   **Features:**
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839473Z  INFO docgen:   Line 35:         *   A filter section with checkboxes or a dropdown menu to select dietary restrictions.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839486Z  INFO docgen:   Line 36:         *   Supported dietary restrictions: Vegetarian, Vegan, Gluten-Free, Dairy-Free, Keto, Paleo. (This list can be expanded).
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839498Z  INFO docgen:   Line 37:         *   Recipes displayed should only include those compliant with the selected filters.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839508Z  INFO docgen:   Line 38: *   **3.3 Recipe Details View**
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839519Z  INFO docgen:   Line 39:     *   **User Story:** As a user, I want to view detailed information about a recipe (ingredients, instructions, nutritional information) so that I can decide if I want to make it.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839531Z  INFO docgen:   Line 40:     *   **Features:**
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839543Z  INFO docgen:   Line 41:         *   Dedicated recipe page displaying:
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839555Z  INFO docgen:   Line 42:             *   Recipe Title
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839567Z  INFO docgen:   Line 43:             *   Ingredients List (with quantities)
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839578Z  INFO docgen:   Line 44:             *   Step-by-step Instructions
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839590Z  INFO docgen:   Line 45:             *   Nutritional Information (calories, macronutrients per serving - data pulled from API)
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839601Z  INFO docgen:   Line 46:             *   Cuisine Type
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839612Z  INFO docgen:   Line 47:             *   Dish Type
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839623Z  INFO docgen:   Line 48:             *   User Rating (initially not available)
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839635Z  INFO docgen:   Line 49:         *   "Save Recipe" button (requires user login - implemented in a later version).
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839648Z  INFO docgen:   Line 50: *   **3.4 User Registration/Login (Basic)**
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839658Z  INFO docgen:   Line 51:     *   **User Story:** As a new user, I want to be able to create an account.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839676Z  INFO docgen:   Line 52:     *   **User Story:** As a returning user, I want to be able to log in.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839687Z  INFO docgen:   Line 53:     *   **Features:**
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839697Z  INFO docgen:   Line 54:         *   Registration form with email and password fields.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839707Z  INFO docgen:   Line 55:         *   Login form with email and password fields.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839718Z  INFO docgen:   Line 56: *   **3.5 Recipe Recommendations (Basic)**
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839729Z  INFO docgen:   Line 57:     *   **User Story:** As a user, I want to see a list of recommended recipes so that I can discover new dishes I might like.
2025-03-02T10:11:14.839740Z  INFO docgen:   Line 58:     *   **Features:**
