2025-03-02T10:44:16.639780Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 15: *   Offer core PDF viewing functionalities, including zoom, navigation, and search.
2025-03-02T10:44:16.639827Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 16: *   Ensure reliable performance and stability across different devices and PDF files.
