2025-03-02T10:44:36.811341Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 21: *   **Students:** Reading textbooks, research papers, and assignments.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.811356Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 22: *   **Professionals:** Reviewing reports, contracts, presentations, and technical documentation.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.811371Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 23: *   **General users:** Accessing ebooks, manuals, forms, and other PDF documents on the go.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.811386Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 24: 
