2025-03-02T10:44:36.813277Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 147: 
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813291Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 148: *   **Performance:**
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813306Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 149:     *   The app should load PDF documents quickly (under 3 seconds for files under 10MB).
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813321Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 150:     *   Page rendering should be smooth and maintain 60 FPS (frames per second) during scrolling and zooming.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813336Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 151:     *   Minimize memory usage to prevent crashes on low-end devices.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813351Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 152: *   **Usability:**
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813366Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 153:     *   The app should be easy to use and intuitive for users of all technical skill levels.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813382Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 154:     *   The UI should be clean, uncluttered, and visually appealing.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813397Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 155:     *   Adhere to platform-specific design guidelines (Material Design for Android, Human Interface Guidelines for iOS).
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813412Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 156: *   **Stability:**
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813428Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 157:     *   The app should be stable and not crash under normal usage conditions.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813448Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 158:     *   Implement robust error handling to prevent crashes due to unexpected input or network issues.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813463Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 159: *   **Security:**
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813479Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 160:     *   The app should handle PDF files securely and prevent vulnerabilities such as buffer overflows or code injection.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813494Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 161:     *   Implement appropriate security measures to protect user data.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813509Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 162: *   **Accessibility:**
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813525Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 163:     *   Provide support for screen readers and other accessibility tools.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813540Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 164:     *   Ensure sufficient contrast between text and background colors.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813555Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 165:     *   Provide alternative text for images.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813570Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 166: *   **Scalability:**
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813584Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 167:     *   The architecture should be scalable to accommodate future features and enhancements.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813600Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 168: *   **Localization:**
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813614Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 169:     *   Prepare the app for future localization to support multiple languages.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813628Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 170: 
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813641Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 171: **6. Open Issues and Risks**
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813655Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 172: 
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813668Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 173: *   Performance with very large PDF files (e.g., over 100MB).  Investigate techniques such as tile-based rendering and lazy loading to optimize performance.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813683Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 174: *   Compatibility with different PDF versions and encodings, especially those with unusual fonts or encryption.  Extensive testing with a variety of PDF files is required.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813696Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 175: *   Potential limitations of the `pdfx` package. Evaluate alternative PDF rendering libraries if necessary (e.g., native platform libraries via Flutter Platform Channels).
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813713Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 176: *   Memory management, especially when dealing with large PDF documents.  Implement proper resource management to avoid memory leaks and out-of-memory errors.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813735Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 177: *   Handling complex PDF features such as annotations, forms, and embedded multimedia. Determine which features are essential and prioritize accordingly.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813758Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 178: *   Search performance on larger documents.
2025-03-02T10:44:36.813779Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 179: 
