2025-03-02T10:44:47.446738Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 41: **Component Descriptions and Responsibilities:**
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446752Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 42: 
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446767Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 43: *   **Flutter UI:** This component is the user interface built using the Flutter framework.
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446781Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 44:     *   Responsibilities:
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446795Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 45:         *   Presenting the PDF document to the user.
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446809Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 46:         *   Handling user input (gestures, button presses, text input).
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446823Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 47:         *   Displaying the page number, zoom level, and search results.
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446837Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 48:         *   Orchestrating calls to the PDF Viewer Core.
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446851Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 49:         *   Displaying loading and error indicators.
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446866Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 50:         *   Provides the "Open PDF", "Open from URL", Search, and Navigation Dialog UI components.
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446880Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 51:         *   Handles text copy to the `System Clipboard`.
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446894Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 52: *   **PDF Viewer Core:** This component acts as the central orchestrator and business logic handler for the PDF viewer.
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446908Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 53:     *   Responsibilities:
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446924Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 54:         *   Managing the PDF document lifecycle (loading, unloading).
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446938Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 55:         *   Coordinating page navigation and zoom operations.
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446952Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 56:         *   Handling search requests (if the search feature is implemented).
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446966Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 57:         *   Exposing an API for the Flutter UI to interact with.
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446980Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 58:         *   Handling errors from the rendering engine, file access, and download manager.
2025-03-02T10:44:47.446995Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 59: *   **PDF Rendering Engine (pdfx or alternative):** This component is responsible for rendering the PDF document's content.
