2025-03-02T10:45:04.562851Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 100:         *   Displaying the page number, zoom level, and search results.
2025-03-02T10:45:04.562864Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 101:         *   Orchestrating calls to the PDF Viewer Core.
2025-03-02T10:45:04.562879Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 102:         *   Displaying loading and error indicators.
