2025-03-02T10:45:04.562922Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 105:     *   **PDF Viewer Widget (A1):** Displays the rendered PDF pages, handles user gestures (zoom, pan, scroll), and manages the viewport.
2025-03-02T10:45:04.562938Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 106:     *   **Control Panel Widget (A2):**  Provides controls for page navigation (next, previous, go to page), zoom level, and opening the search and navigation dialogs.
2025-03-02T10:45:04.562953Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 107:     *   **Navigation Dialog Widget (A3):** Allows the user to quickly jump to a specific page using a number input or a visual page thumbnail preview (if implemented).
2025-03-02T10:45:04.562968Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 108:     *   **Search Dialog Widget (A4):** Provides a text input field for searching within the PDF document and displays search results.
2025-03-02T10:45:04.562983Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 109:     *   **Error/Loading Indicators (A5):** Displays appropriate messages to the user during loading or when errors occur.
2025-03-02T10:45:04.562998Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 110: *   **PDF Viewer Core:** (Expanded) Acts as the central orchestrator and business logic handler for the PDF viewer.
2025-03-02T10:45:04.563012Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 111:     *   Responsibilities:
2025-03-02T10:45:04.563027Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 112:         *   Managing the PDF document lifecycle (loading, unloading).
2025-03-02T10:45:04.563042Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 113:         *   Coordinating page navigation and zoom operations.
2025-03-02T10:45:04.563056Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 114:         *   Handling search requests.
