2025-03-02T10:45:04.563732Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 160: 7.  The **File Access (D)** passes the PDF file to the **PDF Document Manager (B1)** in the **PDF Viewer Core (B)**.
2025-03-02T10:45:04.563746Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 161: 8.  The **PDF Document Manager (B1)** passes the PDF file to the **PDF Rendering Engine (C)**, specifically the **Rendering Pipeline (C1)**.
2025-03-02T10:45:04.563761Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 162: 9.  The **Rendering Pipeline (C1)** uses the **Tile Manager (C3)** to render the visible tiles of the PDF page.
2025-03-02T10:45:04.563775Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 163: 10. The rendered tiles are displayed in the **PDF Viewer Widget (A1)**.
