2025-03-02T10:45:04.563952Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 175: *   **Decomposition of Components:** The Flutter UI, PDF Viewer Core, File Access, and Download Manager components have been further decomposed into smaller, more specific sub-components (e.g., PDF Viewer Widget, Control Panel Widget, PDF Document Manager, File Picker (Native), HTTP Client).
2025-03-02T10:45:04.563967Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 176: *   **Detailed Responsibilities:**  The responsibilities of each component have been further refined to provide a more granular understanding of their functionality.
