2025-03-02T11:13:02.178690Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 126: 
2025-03-02T11:13:02.178708Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 127: *   **Performance:** The app should load PDF documents quickly (under 2 seconds for most documents) and render pages smoothly (at least 30 FPS).  Optimize memory usage to prevent crashes with large files.
2025-03-02T11:13:02.178726Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 128: *   **Usability:** The app should be easy to use and intuitive, with a clean and uncluttered interface. Conduct user testing to identify usability issues.
2025-03-02T11:13:02.178742Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 129: *   **Stability:** The app should be stable and not crash, even with corrupted or malformed PDF files. Implement robust error handling.
2025-03-02T11:13:02.178761Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 130: *   **Security:** The app should handle PDF files securely and prevent vulnerabilities, such as buffer overflows or code injection attacks.  Sanitize all user inputs.
2025-03-02T11:13:02.178778Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 131: *   **Accessibility:** The app should be accessible to users with disabilities, adhering to WCAG guidelines.
2025-03-02T11:13:02.178794Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 132: 
