2025-03-02T11:13:02.178827Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 134: 
2025-03-02T11:13:02.178844Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 135: *   Performance with very large PDF files (over 100MB). Mitigation: Implement memory optimization techniques, lazy loading, and caching.
2025-03-02T11:13:02.178863Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 136: *   Compatibility with different PDF versions and encodings. Mitigation: Thorough testing with a variety of PDF files. Consider using a more robust PDF rendering library if `pdfx` proves insufficient.
2025-03-02T11:13:02.178880Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 137: *   Potential limitations of the `pdfx` package. Mitigation: Evaluate alternative PDF rendering packages.
2025-03-02T11:13:02.178897Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 138: *   Security vulnerabilities in PDF files. Mitigation: Implement security measures to prevent exploitation of vulnerabilities.
2025-03-02T11:13:02.178913Z  INFO docgen::pipeline:   Line 139: *   Support for password-protected PDFs.
